item.description: Exploring the Wonders of Delhi Delhi, the bustling capital of India, is a city where history, culture, and modernity coexist in perfect harmony. From ancient monuments to vibrant markets and delectable street food, Delhi has something for every traveler. Join me on a journey through the heart of India! Day 1: Historical Marvels Red Fort The Red Fort, a UNESCO World Heritage Site, is a symbol of India’s rich history. Its stunning red sandstone architecture and intricate designs are awe-inspiring.
